{"tid":412382,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得就算一個人對外人幾好，對屋企人差咩都係假","createTime":"2017-09-24T15:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T12:39:32.000Z","uid":53197,"like":47,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3586cb50a1fc6ea7af01081b18d80e3046f946e3","tid":412382,"uid":53197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"對父母呼呼喝喝<br />\n講野語氣差<br />\n十問九唔應<br />\n當人透明<br />\n話你一兩句就大大聲鬧返佢地轉頭<br />\n呢d係我眼中都係對屋企人態度差<br />\n<br />\n父母自細對你差嘅話都仲可以理解 <br />\n但如果一直都係對你關懷備至<br />\n你大個左輪到你去照顧返佢地嘅時候<br />\n係咪都應該以呢種方式對返佢地呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俗d講句 父母與生俱來就對你好唔代表唔使珍惜 <br />\n今日唔知聽日事<br />\n唔好等冇左先黎後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n利申：前兩日睇完深水埗單新聞同今日同班親戚食飯後有感"},{"pid":"4c25f8c63b4db9c32e6594d397ceaf0270b1c6b4","tid":412382,"uid":143645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"我就係用一段感情明白以前對屋企人有幾差"},{"pid":"211052780a363fc0f087b3ab1dd6f4dbc2d48687","tid":412382,"uid":53197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就係用一段感情明白以前對屋企人有幾差</blockquote><br />\n而家識對返佢地好就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492cb8c9c699d8d4c0bc97412d7b343525143d89","tid":412382,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:26:02.000Z","msg":"me"},{"pid":"317f8707cbd44bc2b7d6de5e75f11be2b958bf32","tid":412382,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:26:33.000Z","msg":"因為屋企人實在太叻太寸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c95be44002b3b94111b0e5024e30f0da104864","tid":412382,"uid":114062,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:27:44.000Z","ms